name: Gathering at PickNik!
description: Join us in person at PickNik Robotics in Boulder for an evening of networking, seeing cool robots, and speakers! There will be snacks and beverages and this is a great chance to get out there! I can't wait to see everyone. All are welcome!

name: Women in Robotics Coffee by the Bridge
description: Come have a casual coffee and chat with members of Women in Robotics on a gorgeous day in SF by the ocean!
